item.title: [HIVE-22844] Validate cm configs, add retries in fs apis for cm
item.description:
1. Retry create cm root logic
  2. Rename encryptionZones to cmRootLocations to be more accurate
  3. Check cmRootEncrypted.isAbsolute() first before we go for creating anything
  4. Validate fallbackNonEncryptedCmRootDir if it's really not encrypted
  5. Refactor deleteTableData logic
item.summary: Validate cm configs, add retries in fs apis for cm
